        "element": "span",
        "class": "cmt_word",
        "text": "This is the offering - gold and silver and brass",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Gold was needed for the overlaying of the boards, whereof the ark was composed (ver. 11); for the \"crown of gold,\" which surmounted it (",
        "children": []
